	<div id="main">	
	
	   <div id="all_content"> 

	     <div class="MainNewsTitle">
	     <h1>西藏民族大学附属医院超市项目竞争性磋商公告</h1>
	     </div>
				    <div class="MainNewsUpdate">
				      发布时间：2022-11-12
				      
				      信息来源：附属医院　　浏览次数：37905 </div>
				    <div class="MainNewsAction" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;">
				      <script type="text/javascript">writeColor("common/scripts/color/");</script>
				      【<a href="javascript:doZoom('16px');">大</a> <a href="javascript:doZoom('14px');">中</a> <a href="javascript:doZoom('12px');">小</a>】【<a href="javascript:printWindow();">打印本页</a>】【<a href="javascript:closeWindow();">关闭窗口</a>】</div>
				    <div class="MainNewsAction">
				      
         </div>
				    <div class="MainNewsContent" id="content" style="table-layout:fixed;">&nbsp;<b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">一、采购条件</span></b>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">西藏民族大学附属医院</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">综合楼已经启用，为</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">给医院职工、</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">患者</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">及其家属提供一个良好的</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">就医感受</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">，医院研究决定，现就西藏民族大学附属医院新综合楼</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">超市项目</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">面向社会</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">进行竞争性磋商</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">二、项目概况及采购内容</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1、项目概况：西藏民族大学附属医院超市项目位于咸阳市渭城区文汇东路医院综合楼内，建筑面积约 2</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">4</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">㎡</font> <font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、采购内容：引进社会信誉好、有完整保供体系的商超，满足我院员工及患者日常生活所需。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3、本次投标最低报价</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1200</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">元</font><font face="宋体">/月，投标报价低于最低价按无效投标处理。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">所售商品不能高于西藏民族大学校内超市商品零售价格。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">4.经营期限：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;<font face="宋体">年（经营期满</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">后</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">考核</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">合格</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">可续签</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;<font face="宋体">年）</font> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">三、供应商资格要求</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1、具备有效的企业营业执照，经营范围：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:15.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">（</font><font face="宋体">1）一般项目：预包装食品及散装食品；生活日用百货；文体办公用品；鲜花水果、食品、成品饮料等商品。（依法须经批准的项目，经相关部门批准后方可开展经营活动）</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:15.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">（</font><font face="宋体">2）不得经营范围：危险品（如鞭炮等）、代乳制品、烟酒、一次性医疗、护理、康复等用品及自费耗材，不得经营生鲜净菜。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、法定代表人直接参加磋商，须出具法定代表人身份证，非法定代表人参加磋商，须出具法定代表人授权书及被授权人身份证；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3、本项目不接受联合体。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.1000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">四、竞争性磋商响应文件获取方式：</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1、磋商响应文件递交截止时间：已报名的供应商请于2022年</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">11</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">月</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">17</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">日上午</font><font face="宋体">9:30-10：00（北京时间）将投标文件送至西藏民族附属医院</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">综合楼一楼大厅</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">；如因疫情等因素变化使项目变动的，另行通知。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、联系电话：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">18700028356</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">联系人：宋明伟</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;&#10;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3、磋商时间： </span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2022</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;<font face="宋体">年</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">11</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;<font face="宋体">月</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">18</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;<font face="宋体">日上午</font><font face="宋体">10:00（北京时间）</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">4、磋商地点：西藏民族附属医院</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">综合楼十七楼</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">017室</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:225.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:15.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 西藏民族大学附属医院</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="15" style="text-indent:240.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:16.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2022年11月12日</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></p></div>
